    61	- Prevention step for the future: when a new live-capable seam is added, extend the `fullyInjectedDI` allowlist in the SAME slice — the guard is an enumerated allowlist, not structural, so it does NOT auto-cover new seams. The "exempt" regression case is the canary: if a new seam is added and the all-DI exempt case still passes with the old hook set, the allowlist is stale.
    62	- Files changed: `lib/agents/loop/orchestrator.ts`, `lib/agents/router.ts`, `evals/agent-loop.test.ts`, `evals/router.test.ts`; records `docs/reviews/codex-2026-06-28-a3-batch-confirm.md` + `a3-batch-reconcile-evidence.log` (+ 6 gate/review docs stamped DISCHARGED / SHIP 5/5).
