- [docs/e4-entity-resolution-preregistration.md:43](/Users/sharan_98/Desktop/curbside-commons/docs/e4-entity-resolution-preregistration.md:43) — Corpus quotas do not require minimum SAME/general-DIFFERENT denominators or mutually exclusive label/class counts, so precision/recall can be undefined or supported by a trivially small population. Fix: pre-register minimum counts by ground-truth label × class, nonzero denominators, and hard failure for undefined metrics.

