- [app/cost/page.tsx:64](/Users/sharan_98/Desktop/curbside-commons/app/cost/page.tsx:64) — “The complete ledger” and “no unrecorded runs” are false/unprovable: `RUN_RECORDS` omits the 2026-07-05 DEFER calibration and numerous other recorded live judge runs, while legacy Gemini is outside the claimed list. Fix: call these “selected recorded execution legs” and remove exhaustive wording, or construct a genuinely complete ledger.

- [playwright.artifact.config.ts:24](/Users/sharan_98/Desktop/curbside-commons/playwright.artifact.config.ts:24) — `reuseExistingServer: !process.env.CI` lets local/release-gate runs silently test any stale listener on port 3200 instead of the immutable `out/`, defeating artifact-mode provenance. Fix: always launch a fresh artifact server, preferably on an isolated port with a positive artifact-server identity check.

